    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a twisted reflection of your home — a limbo.<br>Explore it, solve its puzzles, meet the spirit of the Keeper, and find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/66e4adce854821f75b52ddd5ec9ea816.poster.avif?t=1755808933\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/66e4adce854821f75b52ddd5ec9ea816.webm?t=1755808933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/66e4adce854821f75b52ddd5ec9ea816.mp4?t=1755808933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mirrors guide you forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But the longer you look, the more cursed you become — and the Keeper won’t let that go unnoticed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/7ac05b8dd863b73e88be049ed172e5f8.poster.avif?t=1755808933\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/7ac05b8dd863b73e88be049ed172e5f8.webm?t=1755808933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/7ac05b8dd863b73e88be049ed172e5f8.mp4?t=1755808933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric puzzles that mix a bit of logic and observation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A curse mechanic tied to how you use mirrors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden rooms, secrets, and fragments of your past</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The satisfaction of actually finishing a game in one sitting</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/1e9f612fca87cbd94d9d202c4c8c0edd.avif?t=1755808933\" width=600 height=256 /></span></p>",
